articles.author: Andrew Wu, Daniel Brettig
articles.title: ‘I haven’t given up’: Why Maxwell, Inglis have moved up in the Test queue - Sydney Morning Herald
articles.description: Glenn Maxwell remains very much in selectors’ Test plans, while wicketkeeper Josh Inglis’ stocks have surged.
articles.content:
Maxwell will be 36 when the Australians are due to tour Sri Lanka in early 2025, an age when many would expect him to be one of the most prized guns for hire on the international Twenty20 circuit.
